name: Dub
body:
### Dub Project -- Tim's Fork
This is my own fork of Gaspard Bucher's (@gaspard) Dub Project. It includes a few things not yet in the parent repository. In particular you'll find some Windows support -- I build and run on Windows.
tagline: A Lua bindings generator that uses Doxygen parsed C/C++ code.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
